Description:
	Creates a rollup config file and updates the gulpfile to include a rollup task.

Example:
    yo gulp-b:rollup

    This will create:
        rollup.config.js

    This will update:
        gulpfile.js with a rollup task to

	package.json to include the following packages:
  	    vinyl-source-stream
	    vinyl-buffer
	    rollup-plugin-node-resolve
	    rollup-plugin-commonjs
	    rollup-stream 
	    rollup-plugin-postcss


	    
